Author:  McKENZIE
Vol / Page:  44
Edition:
Quote:  At this time it was decided to have a movable scaffold capable of being transported to wherever required ...A later version of this contraption became known as the Meccano Set - a term used in official telegrams - `Meccano Set arrived safely and erected'. <i>Ibid.</i> 73 Suitable secrecy surrounded the arrival of the completed scaffold and a telegram went to Head Office, Justice Department, that the `Meccano Set' had arived safely.
