Quote:  Between 1951 and 1957, eight men were hanged on a gallows called the "Meccano Set", built by the Department of Works in the Hutt Valley... Radio New Zealand producers.. collected the stories of the survivors among the witnesses to those executions for their feature, <i>The Meccano Set</i>, which they describe as a collective memory of the rituals of the gallows...
